{"tid":2218490,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"轟醫局白色恐怖 擬統一覆審查信  罷工醫護：共進退抗清算","createTime":"2020-09-26T08:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T08:54:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2f04d6e228153715340cfffeaf88385bb0f89b48","tid":2218490,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T08:54:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200926/S6XKHEBZSRBIRHGNXYO7KHZQSQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200926%2FS6XKHEBZSRBIRHGNXYO7KHZQSQ%2F&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTuzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=dc1c679d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200926%2FS6XKHEBZSRBIRHGNXYO7KHZQSQ%2F&h=84126156\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200926/S6XKHEBZSRBIRHGNXYO7KHZQSQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n轟醫局白色恐怖 擬統一覆審查信 <br />\n罷工醫護：共進退抗清算<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HsGCnrATOc9XCroAAvFlJNiDgIc=/1848x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LRRWO5S4MVESHOOOTE2F35EZVM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHsGCnrATOc9XCroAAvFlJNiDgIc%3D%2F1848x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLRRWO5S4MVESHOOOTE2F35EZVM.jpg&h=113c4d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■年初逾7,000名醫護罷工要求政府封關。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】林鄭政府至今未有為今年初堅拒封關致疫情大爆發而致歉，反而向發起罷工力促政府「封關」的逾7,000名醫護人員步步進逼。醫管局主席范鴻齡前日表示將發信予數千名曾參加行動的醫護，要求他們解釋「缺勤」原因；工會昨日隨即反擊，向會員發表公開信派定心丸，重申罷工「合情、合理、合法」，呼籲員工收到信件後切勿個別回覆，工會將諮詢法律團隊統一處理，更聲言不排除會發起集體抗議行動。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：大狀：工會行動受法律保障<br />\n<br />\n醫管局員工陣線昨早在專頁刊登一篇題為「告會員的信：存亡之秋 共同進退」信件，內容提及《基本法》第27條列明，香港居民享有參加工會、罷工的權利和自由。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斥「只處理提出問題的人」<br />\n<br />\n工會2月發起罷工後，特首林鄭月娥除了將發起罷工的醫護工會形容為「害群之馬」，更明言醫護採取罷工手法迫使政府答應訴求是「不會得逞」。工會於信中直斥，政府只以政治掛帥，更抹黑醫護人員為「極端分子」，又批評政府以豁免檢疫方式容許跨境人士入境播毒，令香港第三波疫情爆發，奪去過百名港人生命。<br />\n<br />\n信中亦提到，工會於發動罷工前已諮詢律師團隊意見，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n工會於文末強調，醫護人員必須團結一致，作為發起罷工的工會，保障會員權益絕對責無旁貸，「存亡之秋，讓我們一起共進退」。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局員工陣線副主席羅卓堯指，暫時未有人收到醫管局的相關信件，未知內容會否提及解僱等懲處字眼，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n羅指工會後續行動須視乎信件內容，現計劃呼籲如有員工收到信件切勿個別回覆，工會將諮詢法律團隊統一處理，又警告如局方發信後再作進一步清算，將與會員協商發起集體抗議行動。<br />\n<br />\n另外昨日立法會財委會會議上，有議員質問醫管局追究醫護動用的法律開支，醫管局行政總裁高拔陞稱暫未能交代。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VbkbF-hthNukLvA2Klyd5WAM98M=/1216x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GKDK2S73JBBVRPDF3755JUMRUY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVbkbF-hthNukLvA2Klyd5WAM98M%3D%2F1216x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGKDK2S73JBBVRPDF3755JUMRUY.jpg&h=bbad8123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅卓堯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/i_j1lJZ3wRxYfXxpGfRbMZ1afWU=/1305x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FLOO66HA3BFWLB2WNLYJJYVADU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fi_j1lJZ3wRxYfXxpGfRbMZ1afWU%3D%2F1305x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFLOO66HA3BFWLB2WNLYJJYVADU.jpg&h=da55f911&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n范鴻齡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/p6G8dMR30BDKQhkJAv5pISOw3r8=/887x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AQRYVOJCHJHOXCQUUONZBOUYHI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fp6G8dMR30BDKQhkJAv5pISOw3r8%3D%2F887x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAQRYVOJCHJHOXCQUUONZBOUYHI.jpg&h=8a60d47b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■員工陣線昨向會員發公開信籲集體抗議醫管局打壓。 員工陣線IG圖片"}]}